Installing the phyglos catalog in the BANDIT toolkit
====================================================

Download the latest version of the phyglos catalog from phyglos.org
$ wget ftp://phyglos.org/catalogs/phyglos 
$ tar xvf phyglos

As root, copy the bundles and origins directories into the $BANDIT_HOME/etc directory
# cd phyglos-x.y.z
# mv bundles $BANDIT_HOME/etc
# mv origins $BANDIT_HOME/etc
# chown -R root.root $BANDIT_HOME/etc
